---
import "../styles/global.css";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
    <h1>2026</h1>
    (@apata)
    <details class="work-item">
        <summary><span class="marker">▸</span> 3DS Server Runtime</summary>
        <p>
            As a team of two designed and implemented a 3DS Server runtime in Kotlin, capable of passing FIME certification test suites across all current 3DS protocol versions.
            Translated EMVCo specifications into executable authentication flows under strict certification constraints and compressed delivery timelines.
        </p>

        <ul>
            <li>Kotlin</li>
            <li>Spring Boot</li>
            <li>Postgres, jOOQ, Flyway</li>
        </ul>
    </details>

    <details class="work-item">
        <summary><span class="marker">▸</span> Async Job Worker Pool</summary>
        <p>
            Implemented a distributed job execution service for handling asynchronous workloads. Designed the service to function as
            a general purpose pool of compute for all async application jobs across the application, with controlled concurrency and isolated processing.
            This enabled scalable compute for batch processing and long-running background jobs.
        </p>

        <ul>
            <li>Typescript, Node.js</li>
            <li>AWS (ECS, SQS)</li>
            <li>Terraform</li>
            <li>Redis</li>
        </ul>
    </details>

    <details class="work-item">
        <summary><span class="marker">▸</span> Core AWS SDK Migration</summary>
        <p>
            Migrated core infrastructure from AWS SDK v2 to v3 across heavily used services, including S3 integrations forming a significant portion of system dependencies.
            Refactored client injection patterns and introduced safe rollout mechanisms to eliminate legacy security vulnerabilities.
        </p>

        <ul>
            <li>TypeScript</li>
            <li>AWS SDK</li>
            <li>S3</li>
            <li>Feature Flags</li>
        </ul>
    </details>

    <details class="work-item">
        <summary><span class="marker">▸</span> Accessibility Audit CLI</summary>
        <p>
            Built an automated CLI for WCAG 2.1 accessibility validation across large sets of HTML templates using automated rule-based analysis.
            Enabled batch auditing, CI integration, and structured reporting for large-scale remediation of accessibility issues.
        </p>

        <ul>
            <li>Node.js</li>
            <li>axe-core</li>
            <li>CI/CD</li>
            <li>HTML</li>
        </ul>
    </details>

    <details class="work-item">
        <summary><span class="marker">▸</span> Analytics Platform Expansion</summary>
        <p>
            Delivered multi-tab analytics interfaces providing structured visibility into transaction, integration, and third-party processing data.
            Implemented backend and frontend components under shifting requirements while maintaining delivery continuity across multiple workstreams.
        </p>

        <ul>
            <li>TypeScript</li>
            <li>React</li>
            <li>Node.js</li>
            <li>PostgreSQL</li>
        </ul>
    </details>
    <br>

    <h1>2025</h1>
</Layout>
